 《全面战争：法老》有一个专门讲心计的“游戏中的游戏” https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-pharaoh-has-a-board-game-inspired-game-within-a-game-3497339?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=total-战争法老有一款受棋盘游戏启发的游戏中的游戏Andy BrownWed, 13 Sep 2023 12:06:11 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsGamescom 2023PC https://www.nme.com/?p=3497339 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="全面战争：法老。图片来源：创意大会。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>埃及法院是“让自己摆脱困境的工具箱”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-pharaoh-has-a-board-game-inspired-game-within-a-game-3497339">《全面战争：法老》后有一款致力于策划的“游戏中的游戏”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="全面战争：法老。图片来源：创意大会。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/total-war-pharaoh">《全面战争：法老</a></em><em>》</em>导演托多尔·尼科洛夫 (Todor Nikolov) 在接受 NME 采访时表示，即将推出的策略游戏的埃及法庭功能将成为“游戏中的游戏”，让玩家策划自己的权力之路。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/best-strategy-games-3199564">2023 年最佳策略游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p>与更广泛的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/total-war">《全面战争》</a></em>系列一致， <em>《法老王》</em>将要求玩家征服回合制战役地图，同时在实时战斗中操纵军队。但历史策略有一个新特点：埃及法庭，它让<em>全面战争的</em>粉丝们可以尝试政治。</p><p>在这里，玩家可以赢得宫廷中最有影响力的人物——比如宗教领袖或财务主管——的青睐，以换取丰厚的奖励，或者密谋勒索对手，甚至篡夺他们的地位。在讨论该功能时，尼科洛夫透露，开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/creative-assembly">Creative Assembly</a>希望为玩家提供更多与游戏中其他派系互动的方式。</p><p> “这是游戏中的游戏，”尼科洛夫分享道。 “它的灵感来自于许多棋盘游戏，这是我们在<em>《全面战争》</em>中添加的一个新东西，因为这些角色不属于你的阵营。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="全面战争：法老 - 战役地图天桥" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ftntuRG2yn4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “整个事情可以用作一个工具箱，让你摆脱困境，”他补充道。 “我不止一次能够保卫一座城市，只是因为我与[埃及]高级指挥官关系良好，他给我派了一些部队。这是定制、建立和发展你的派系的一种有趣的方式。”</p><p><em>法老王</em>的法庭系统并不是唯一增加战役地图深度的功能。该游戏还标志着<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/a-total-war-saga-troy">《全面战争传奇：特洛伊》</a></em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6VQdVYQoT0g" target="_blank" rel="noopener">基于资源的经济</a>的回归，该经济要求玩家在货币之外管理石头和食物等物品。</p><p> Nikolov 解释说，Creative Assembly 希望“进一步探索和开发”该系统，并认为它“与<em>法老</em>的设计时期和故事相关”。</p><p> “这种动态与我们在<em>特洛伊</em>看到的情况非常不同，”他们说。 “例如，如果你想正确地发展你的定居点和建筑，拥有石头就非常重要，所以你需要考虑到在你的战役进行到一定阶段后，石头会变得稀疏。”</p><p>除了<em>《全面战争：</em><em>法老》</em>之外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-warhammer-3-will-make-ai-factions-smarter-and-less-biased-3491045"><em>《全面战争：战锤 3》的</em>最新更新</a>也使其 AI 派系变得“更聪明”，并且不太可能骚扰玩家。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-pharaoh-has-a-board-game-inspired-game-within-a-game-3497339">《全面战争：法老》后有一款致力于策划的“游戏中的游戏”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
碧昂斯的舞者与试图向她扔物体的粉丝对峙https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-dancers-confront-fan-who-tried- throw-object-at-her-3497318?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=beyonces-dancers-confront-fan-谁试图向她扔物体Tom SkinnerWed, 13 Sep 2023 12:04:29 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3497318 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/beyonce-london-2023-getty-.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="碧昂斯在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/beyonce-london-2023-getty-.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/beyonce-london-2023-getty--400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/beyonce-london-2023-getty--800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/beyonce-london-2023-getty--696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/beyonce-london-2023-getty--1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/beyonce-london-2023-getty--1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>中断发生时，这位歌手正在表演《Drunk In Love》</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-dancers-confront-fan-who-tried-throw-object-at-her-3497318">碧昂丝的舞者与试图向她扔物体的粉丝对峙的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/beyonce-london-2023-getty-.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="碧昂斯在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/beyonce-london-2023-getty-.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/beyonce-london-2023-getty--400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/beyonce-london-2023-getty--800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/beyonce-london-2023-getty--696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/beyonce-london-2023-getty--1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/beyonce-london-2023-getty--1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在最近的一场<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-renaissance-review-tracklist-artwork-3278806">“文艺复兴”</a>演出中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯</a>的两名伴舞与一名向舞台投掷物体的粉丝发生冲突 - 请查看下面的镜头。</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/beyonce-break-my-soul-track-review-renaissance-big-freedia-3252593">“Break My Soul”</a>歌手目前正在北美巡演，他是最新一位成为流行趋势受害者的艺术家之一，这种流行趋势中，现场观众试图通过扔东西来吸引注意力。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/beyonce-live-in-london-setlist-photos-3449559">碧昂丝伦敦演唱会：夏季最耀眼的巡演充满欢乐</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://nypost.com/2023/09/12/beyonces-dancers-rush-to-protect-singer-after-fan-throws-object-onstage/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约邮报》</em></a>报道，在贝伊的一场音乐会上，贝伊的长期舞者劳伦特·布尔乔亚和拉里·尼古拉斯·布尔乔亚（又名“双胞胎”）看到人群中的某人向舞台扔东西后，走近了他们。</p><p>这一时刻被粉丝拍摄的视频捕捉到，该视频后来在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/tiktok">TikTok</a>上分享。从视频中可以看出，有问题的物体是一件衣服——当碧昂斯表演《Drunk In Love》时，这件衣服落在了她的脚上。</p><p>双胞胎中的一个迅速将物品从舞台上移走，从驻扎着众多保安的摄影师坑里拿到了它。随后，舞者们与肇事者对峙，随后似乎缓和了局势。</p><p>然而，据报道，一名保安人员阻止了球迷第二次投掷物体的尝试，布尔乔亚双胞胎随后回到前排。舞者们似乎与参加者交换了一些严厉的话语，然后就怒气冲冲地离开了。 </p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@travis_in_cali/video/7277582173237021994" data-video-id="7277582173237021994" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 325px;" ><section> <a target="_blank" title="@travis_in_cali" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@travis_in_cali?refer=embed">@travis_in_cali</a></p><p>在舞台上，有东西向碧昂斯投掷，Les Twins 准备战斗。醉在爱中<a title="莱双胞胎" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/lestwins?refer=embed">#lestwins</a> <a title="碧昂丝" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/beyonce?refer=embed">#beyonce</a> <a title="文艺复兴世界巡演" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/renaissanceworldtour?refer=embed">#renaissanceworldtour</a> <a title="复兴" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/reniassance?refer=embed">#reniassance</a> <a title="索菲体育场" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/sofistadium?refer=embed">#sofistadium</a> <a title="洛杉矶" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/losangeles?refer=embed">#losangeles</a></p><p> <a target="_blank" title="♬ 原声 - Travis_in_cali" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7277582289473735467?refer=embed">♬ 原声 – Travis_in_cali</a></section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><p>视频上的说明文字写道：“一定有人很愚蠢，向碧昂斯扔东西！ Le Twins要为此打架了！”观看上面的剪辑。</p><p>在评论部分，一位 TikTok 用户写道：“Les Twins 干得好。是保安人员没有尽到自己的职责。”另一个人说：“人们抱怨说贝只来过中心一次，但这就是原因。她离得越近，风险就越大。”</p><p>第三个人评论道：“白痴，你为什么要在舞台上扔东西？”</p><p>其他受到这一危险趋势影响的艺术家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/harry-styles-penis-hit-by-flying-object-during-chicago-concert-3330933">Harry Styles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-nas-x-pauses-gig-after-fan-throws-sex-toy-on-stage-3464509">Lil Nas X</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-hits-out-at-fan-for-throwing-book-at-his-head-onstage-3485633">Drake</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-throws-microphone-at-audience-member-who-chucked-drink-at-her-on-stage-3475213">Cardi B</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pink-stunned-as-fan-throws-mothers-ashes-onto-stage-at-bst-hyde-park-3461977">Pink</a> 。</p><p>最令人担忧的案例是，在纽约演出<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bebe-rexha-collapses-on-stage-after-being-struck-in-head-by-fans-phone-at-gig-3457928">期间，一名观众将手机扔到</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bebe-rexha">贝比·雷克萨 (Bebe Rehxa)</a>的脸上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bebe-rexha-attacker-reportedly-threw-phone-at-her-head-because-it-would-be-funny-3458236">，因为他认为这会“有趣”，导致她</a>需要缝针。 </p><figure id="attachment_3476889" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3476889" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3476889" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_beyonce_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="碧昂丝" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_beyonce_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3476889" class="wp-caption-text">碧昂斯于 2023 年 7 月 29 日在新泽西州东卢瑟福大都会人寿体育场举行的“文艺复兴”巡演中登台表演。图片来源：Kevin Mazur/Parkwood 的 WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>在其他地方，美国乡村流行歌手凯尔西·巴莱里尼 (Kelsea Ballerini) 被人群向她投掷的物品击中脸部（来自<a href="https://variety.com/2023/music/artists/kelsea-ballerini-hit-object-concert-idaho-bebe-rexha-1235657781/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a> ）。</p><p>许多粉丝和现场表演者谴责那些造成这种破坏的人。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-calls-on-fans-to-stop-throwing-things-at-artists-on-stage-3464740">阿黛尔在 7 月份的一场拉斯维加斯演出中呼吁音乐会观众“停止扔东西”</a> ，并警告说：“我他妈的敢于向我扔东西，我他妈的会杀了你。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-says-fans-throwing-objects-at-performers-is-infuriating-3468291">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-on-fans-throwing-things-at-performers-artists-arent-regarded-as-people-anymore-3479191">科里·泰勒 (Corey Taylor)</a>和凯莉·克拉克森 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-warns-fans-against-throwing-things-onstage-at-las-vegas-residency-3476190">Kelly Clarkson)</a>等人也公开反对在舞台上扔东西的趋势。 “当你在上面时，这绝对令人愤怒，”艾利什说。 “你处于弱势地位。”</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kendrick-lamar-diana-ross-join-beyonce-on-stage-sing-happy-birthday-3493555">碧昂丝上周在洛杉矶的一场演出中邀请肯德里克·拉马尔和戴安娜·罗斯一起庆祝了她的 42 岁生日</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-dancers-confront-fan-who-tried-throw-object-at-her-3497318">碧昂丝的舞者与试图向她扔物体的粉丝对峙的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
根据 Steam 周年庆帖子，《反恐精英 2》“即将”推出https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2-is-launching-soon-according-to-steam-anniversary-post-3497326?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=counter-strike-根据 Steam 周年庆帖子，2 即将推出Imogen DonovanWed, 13 Sep 2023 11:40:00 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3497326 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《反恐精英 2》。图片来源：Valve。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该游戏原定于今年夏天发布</p><p>根据 Steam 周年纪念帖子首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2-is-launching-soon-according-to-steam-anniversary-post-3497326">，“反恐精英 2”帖子“即将”发布</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《反恐精英 2》。图片来源：Valve。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/valve">Valve</a>在庆祝<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/steam">Steam</a> 20 周年的帖子中发布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/counter-strike-2"><em>《反恐精英 2》</em></a>的发布公告。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/assassins-creed-mirage-will-turn-back-time-for-ubisofts-killer-series-3494836">《刺客信条幻影》将逆转育碧杀手系列的时光</a></strong></li></ul><p>此前，开发商表示续作的目标是在夏季发布。然而几个月过去了，Valve 却没有任何关于<em>《反恐精英 2》</em>状态的更新。</p><p>在庆祝 Steam 推出 20 周年之际，Valve 评论了 2023 年的成就以及玩家在不久的将来必须期待的事情。 “这一年还没有结束，”它补充道。</p><p> “到目前为止，我们已经发布了一个巨大的 Steam 客户端更新， <em>《反恐精英 2》</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/valve-shuts-down-fans-trying-to-idle-their-way-into-the-counter-strike-2-test-3421791">进入测试版</a>（并将很快发布），现在有超过 11,000 个游戏在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/steam-deck">Steam Deck</a>上经过验证或可玩，”该公司表示。因此，预计粉丝们将在接下来的几周内了解有关游戏发布的更多信息。 </p><figure id="attachment_3418959" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3418959" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3418959" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-skins.jpg" alt="《反恐精英 2》。图片来源：Valve。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-skins.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-skins-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-skins-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-skins-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-skins-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-skins-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3418959" class="wp-caption-text"> 《反恐精英 2》来源：Valve</figcaption></figure><p> <em>《反恐精英 2》</em>于今年 3 月发布，粉丝们几乎没有注意到它已被列入开发者的议程。 Nvidia 驱动程序的更新<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2-reportedly-getting-public-beta-3408673">发现了名为“csgo2.exe”和“cs2.exe”的文件，</a>但 Valve 当时并未承认这一点。</p><p>然后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2-trademarks-filed-by-developer-valve-3415969"><em>《反恐精英 2》</em>的商标在正式宣布前一周突然出现</a>。虽然标题可能另有暗示，但这并不是<em>《反恐精英》</em>系列中的一款全新游戏。相反，它是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/heres-first-look-valves-iconic-dust-2-map-counter-strike-2-3418910"><em>《全球攻势》</em>的免费升级</a>，被誉为“ <em>《反恐精英</em>》历史上最大的技术飞跃”。</p><p>改进后的版本由 Valve 的 Source 2 引擎组成，包括对烟雾弹和“子更新”等方面的重大更改，这将使“服务器知道运动开始、开枪或投掷‘弹珠’的确切瞬间” 。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bethesda">贝塞斯达</a>的托德·霍华德表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/starfield"><em>《Starfield》</em></a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/starfield-development-had-hundreds-of-plans-that-went-out-the-window-3497302">有“数百个计划”，</a>但这些计划“都被抛到了窗外”，无法满足团队对这款游戏的期望。</p><p>根据 Steam 周年纪念帖子首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2-is-launching-soon-according-to-steam-anniversary-post-3497326">，“反恐精英 2”帖子“即将”发布</a>。</p> ;
 “Top Boy”：夏日别墅的居民说演出“对我们没有任何帮助” https://www.nme.com/news/tv/top-boy-summerhouse-estate-residents-say-show-done-nothing-for-us-3497344?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=top-boy-summerhouse-庄园居民说显示没有为我们做任何事Adam StarkeyWed, 13 Sep 2023 11:32:20 +0000 NewsTV NewsNetflixTop Boy https://www.nme.com/?p=3497344 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="顶级男孩" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这笔钱本来是要返还给居民的，但我认为他们做得不对”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/top-boy-summerhouse-estate-residents-say-show-done-nothing-for-us-3497344">《Top Boy》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="顶级男孩" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>居住在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/top-boy"><em>《Top Boy》</em></a>拍摄地的居民声称这部剧对他们“没有做任何事”。</p><p>在由阿什利·沃尔特斯 (Ashley Walters) 和凯恩·卡诺·罗宾逊 (Kane &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kano">Kano</a> &#39; Robinson) 主演的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>节目中，描绘虚构避暑别墅的场景是在伦敦东部犬岛的萨姆达庄园拍摄的。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/top-boy-review-netflix-3491681">《Top Boy》第五季评论：仍然是 Netflix 上最伟大的电视节目</a></strong></li></ul><p>该庄园的居民在该剧中作为临时演员出现。私人经营的地产管理公司 One Housing 也获得了一笔未公开的金额，以允许使用该地产，这将用于为居住在该地产上的家庭提供前往主题公园或海边的旅行。</p><p>然而，一些人声称他们并没有从这笔钱中感受到任何好处，因为旅行很快就被预订满了，而另一些人则认为这笔钱应该有助于改善庄园的状况。 </p><figure id="attachment_3492139" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3492139" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3492139" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Jaq.jpg" alt="顶级男孩" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Jaq.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Jaq-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Jaq-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Jaq-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Jaq-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Jaq-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3492139" class="wp-caption-text">贾克（Jaq），由贾丝敏·乔布森饰演。图片来源：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p> 52 岁的朱莉·哈钦森 (Julie Hutchinson) 在该庄园生活了 16 年，她 (通过<a href="https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-12508531/Netflix-Boy-summerhouse-estate-gangsters.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>MailOnline</em></a> ) 说：“他们没有为我们做任何事。庄园确实很破旧。他们不做任何工作。</p><p> “One Housing 从拍摄中受益，但真正住在这里的人却没有受益。从事这项工作的人都很好。”</p><p>哈钦森表示，这部讲述毒贩杜尚（沃尔特斯饰）和萨利（卡诺饰）的剧“非常牵强”。</p><p> “这里没有帮派出没之类的，”她补充道。 “这并不能公平地反映这种状态，但也没有试图做到这一点。这是虚构的。但这笔钱本来是要返还给居民的，我认为他们做得不对。他们没有为我们做任何事。”</p><p>特里·威格泽尔（Terry Wigzell）的四个孩子就在那些错过付费旅行的人之列。 “出行真的很困难，”他说。 “一趟去乐高乐园，另一趟去布莱顿。</p><p> “有不少，但我们没能抓住其中任何一个。他们都被填满了。也许他们可以把钱花在所有孩子都可以做的事情上。</p><p> “ <em>Top Boy</em>确实是一件大事。这是命中注定的。但这并没有给我们带来任何好处。”</p><p> A spokesperson for One Housing said it had consulted with residents on how they would like to see the money spent earlier this year – which is contested by those living on the estate.</p><p> “The funding we received for use of the Samuda estate to film <em>Top Boy</em> has contributed to the resident engagement, financial and community support services we offer,” the spokesperson said. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="顶级男孩：第 3 季 |官方预告片 #2 | Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Y0ME5ahl1jQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “It was important to us that we consulted residents at Samuda (around 500 properties) on how they would like to spend the funds.</p><p> “Throughout January and February, we carred out numerous consultations including door-knocking exercises, home visits, phone calls, Freepost return surveys, and approaching established community groups in the area, asking residents to share their ideas.</p><p> “Hearing from them and understanding the current financial challenges faced, we have been able to offer days out that many had shared they were currently unable to experience, such as trips to theme parks during the summer holidays, visits to beaches, and wellbeing activities.”</p><p> One Housing added that it is “continuing to use every opportunity to ensure residents have their say so there is something for everyone”.</p><p> “Trips have been organised on a first come, first served basis at the moment but more activities are being arranged so everyone can have the opportunity to benefit from the funding received,” the spokesperson added.</p><p> In the show&#39;s first two seasons, which originally aired on <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/channel-4">Channel 4</a> , scenes on the Summerhouse estate were shot on the Heygate Estate in Elephant and Castle – which was later demolished in 2014.</p><p> After Channel 4 axed the series in 2013, <em>Top Boy</em> was revived by Netflix in 2019, with help from <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/drake">Drake</a> who served as an executive producer. For the show&#39;s last three seasons, filming moved to the Samuda Estate.</p><p> <em>《Top Boy》</em>可在 Netflix 上观看。</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/top-boy-summerhouse-estate-residents-say-show-done-nothing-for-us-3497344">&#39;Top Boy&#39;: Summerhouse estate residents say show has “done nothing for us”</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
